AbbreviationsTransformations - Class in pl.put.poznan.transformer.logic
An object of this class should be used to edit text: make abbreviations or expand them Abbreviations are based on data read from file and stored in HashMaps: abbr(used to abbreviate whole words) exp(used to expand abbreviations into whole words) String sequence is the text to be tranformed
